  "title": "Head of Sales - Maritime Tech",
  "description": "<p>We are partnering with a dynamically growing technology company in the maritime industry. This role plays a key part in driving sales growth and developing effective sales strategies to expand into new clients and strengthen existing accounts.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Achieve sales targets through strategic planning and execution.</li><li>Identify and pursue new business opportunities, adjusting strategies to local market conditions and customer needs.</li><li>Manage client onboarding and ensure projects are set up effectively.</li><li>Understand client needs and tailor solutions accordingly.</li><li>Collaborate with marketing, product, and customer service teams to deliver integrated solutions.</li><li>Develop and implement market entry plans to grow the company’s presence.</li><li>Conduct market research to track industry trends, competitors, and new opportunities.</li><li>Oversee sales operations including pipeline management, forecasting, and reporting.</li><li>Represent the company at meetings, trade shows, and industry events.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Strong background in sales and client management.</li><li>Proven record of achieving or exceeding sales targets in the maritime industry.</li><li>Network of contacts across shipping companies (ship owners, ship managers, ship operators).</li></ul><p><br /><br /></p><p><em>If you'd like to hear more, please apply and/or contact us at:</em></p><p><em>www.holloberg.com</em></p><p><em>Business Registration No: 201805144D</em></p><p><em>EA Registration No: R1653145</em></p><p><em>License No: 18C9522</em></p>",
